  <brief_title>Defining Late Onset Occult Asymptomatic Cardiotoxicity in Childhood Cancer Survivors Exposed to Anthracycline Therapy</brief_title>
  <official_title>Defining Late Onset Occult Asymptomatic Cardiotoxicity in Childhood Cancer Survivors Exposed to Anthracycline Therapy: A Cardiac Magnetic Resonance and Biomarker Imaging and Serological Biomarker Study</official_title>
